phrases: Okay, I am going to break down the door so we can get out.
Is not that a burglar sensor?
It might bring the security guards here if we break down the door.
All the better if they find us.
You will ruin the school camp.
Besides, if Miku found out about this...
Try to see if you can disarm it.
If only I were two meters tall.
Hurry up and get on my shoulders.
I cannot trip this sensor in my heart, either.
Do not you dare say I am heavy.
It is giving me a weird case of deja vu.
Also, you are too heavy for me to lift.
You went and said it after all!
The Quint es sen tial Quin tup let us
We need a key to disarm the sensor.
Looks like we will have to wait for help.
I am trying to start a fire, obviously.
It will ruin our last day here if we catch a cold.
Futaro-kun's smart, but he is kind of a dummy.
Since there is nothing to do, let us talk about something fun.
She left saying she needed to do campfire group stuff.
Have either of you seen Uesugi-san?
He vanished in the middle of helping the campfire group.
He is not in the dining hall, and he is not in the room.
He is wandered off to waste time again!
Are you sure I can take him?
I guess Big Sis will have to take care of poor, lonely Futaro.
I am going to go look for them.
Yotsuba, what is that key for?
And that is the whole story.
The other day, Itsuki-chan was like...
What do you think she said when she saw that croquette?
You are going to make Big Sis cry again.
He is avoiding asking why I cried.
I wonder if he is just not interested.
Really, why did I cry, anyway?
I would technically be taking a break.
So, you know how I have been shooting for a movie, right?
I am starting to get more gigs now, too.
Other actors playing student roles skip school knowing they will have to retake the year,
or move to more flexible schools.
You know how hopeless I am when it comes to school.
I do not think I would miss high school.
Miku might be better off if I am gone.
You found something you want to do.
But wait, what happens to my pay if you are gone?!
I thought that is how pissed you would be.
Is that how you see me?
I envy you for having options.
Though you are 99 percent likely to fail.
But it will be a good experience.
And if it works out, great.
No need to worry with Ichika.
We can call off the dancing together thing.
It will be our very own campfire tonight.
Well, no one's looking, I guess.
I never knew you had such a cute side.
It is bad enough that there is a rumor about a legend going around.
People will make certain assumptions about us.
Yotsuba told me there is a legend that people who dance at the campfire
The campfire was important to Miku.
If the alarm is not disarmed,
security personnel will be dispatched immediately.
Shoot, we need to get out before someone comes here.
Got To put out the fire.
What were you two doing here?
I had to explain the incident with Ichika to the teachers.
Itsuki and Miku did not fully believe us.
I hope we have another chance to explain.
How did our fun school camp end up like this?
Okay, Miku-chan, we will be in the dining hall.
If we really are all equal,
what am I supposed to do?
I cannot believe I had to get sick now.
Accident or not, it was the result of your carelessness.
Stay in bed for the day and reflect on what you did.
Oh, you do not need to stay with me.
I will meet up with you once I feel better.
Or are you having a hard time facing Futaro-kun?
You have been wary around him ever since our stay at the inn.
It is only been three months.
That day, when I asked him for help with schoolwork at the cafeteria,
I did not have the faintest idea...
that things would come to this.
Does Futaro-kun seem like such a bad person to you?
Th-That is not what I mean.
You are not getting away just because it is an optional activity.
Let us ski down all the slopes!
Sleeping is a waste of time.
If you really cannot ski, I will hold your hands and guide you.
By the way, where is the idiot quartet?
Ichika's sick, and Itsuki's taking care of her.
I guess that is not surprising after what happened.
You should have checked before you locked the door.
You are really hard to tell apart from just your faces.
I am always the one being taught stuff,
but today, I am going to teach you two everything!
Yeah, I am not all better yet, but...
Was not she taking care of you?
Itsuki-chan's skiing on her own because she does not feel like she can face you.
These guys refuse to learn anything I teach them!
That is how I always feel about you!
Let us make it fun, then.
Yotsuba's the best, so she is it.
I am catching them as soon as I find them, obviously.
Damn it, I only just learned to go forward.
Wait, this might be a chance to explain myself to Miku.
When did she get so good?
There is something I want to make sure about.
You have not told anyone about last night, right?
When you teach something, you have to cover everything.
I do not know if it is because I never got Raiha's good luck charm back,
but I have been having crap luck since yesterday.
What kind of weird name is that?
I only ever gave this to you.
That I was lying to her during the test of courage last night?
How do I deal with this amicably?
Did you see a blond guy go your way?
You did not make this, did you?
I-I mean, Yotsuba might still be out there.
Let me stay here for a while longer.
Where does she get that endless stamina, anyway?
It is hard to believe she is really one of you quintuplets.
She would have caught me if this igloo had not been here, too.
How are we going to escape?
Let us get Yotsuba to have a handicap.
We could make her carry things so we can be equally fast.
That will make it more fun, I guess.
But I do not really like that.
The five of you started off with the same physical abilities, did not you?
That means Yotsuba earned her athleticism for herself.
I know this is just a game, but...
I do not want to disregard that effort.
Anyone who does it wants that person all to themselves.
Are you sure I can take him?
No need to worry with Ichika.
What were you two doing here?
but you cannot ignore the work she put in.
Let us be fair, not equal.
What the hell am I saying, anyway?
I am going to get some fresh air.
I am going to find you, no matter what.
There is something I want to talk to you about.
Next Time on The Quintessential Quintuplets
There is no way that is true.
